Class ItemTileMemory

java.lang.Object
it.polimi.ingsw.View.GUI.SceneController.Utility.ItemTileMemory
public class ItemTileMemory extends Object
The ItemTileMemory class is responsible for storing and retrieving information related to item tiles in the GUI.
